      <prereq class="- topic/section task/prereq ">
         <p platform="Modular-DC Modular-AC Prime-UPS Prime-Inverter"
            class="- topic/p ">Every 6 months it is recommended to do a visual check of the system
environment, check readings from the display and condition inside
the door (without removing any protective covers), do a LED test and
perform battery maintenance.<note platform="Modular-DC Modular-AC"
                  type="important"
                  class="- topic/note ">If the battery is installed in the system the protective
covers in front of the battery cells need to be removed for maintenance.</note>
         </p>
         <p platform="Modular-Inverter Modular-DCDC-Converter Prime-Inverter"
            class="- topic/p ">Every 6 months it is recommended to do a visual check of the system
environment, check readings from the display and condition inside
the door (without removing any protective covers) and do a LED test.</p>
